data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Beautiful brick home on an oversized corner lot, with a spacious backyard! This spacious and well thought out floor plan has so much to offer, and is located in a charming neighborhood. The large living space features an abundance of natural light and a floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace. There is ample storage throughout this lovely home. Three large bedrooms, all with large, spacious closets. The kitchen is warm and cheerful, featuring a massive kitchen pantry! Granite throughout. Conveniently located to new medical care facilities, casual and boutique shopping, wonderful dining, and entertainment!
